data.description: Gruene SunHill Log Cabin River Escape!  Minutes away from Gruene Historical district and private subdivision access to the Guadalupe River Park. 3 full bedrooms and three full baths, plus a bonus room, large detached garage and huge covered deck! Deck was added in 2020 and completely rebuilt. New paint and upgrades throughout. Giant oak trees, sits on a curl-de-sac street on almost 2 acres! Close to everything but secluded and private - enjoy wildlife daily including whitetail and turkeys!
